div.div:
Add relative-time tag to input field
Implemented a new 'relative-time' tag to the input field view to handle time inputs. This tag correctly renders elapsed time from the given timestamp. Additionally, a conditional was added to maintain the previous 'datalist' behavior when 'relativeTime' was not used.

Add default cursor and update collaborative session in Quill controller
Added a default cursor initialization in the Quill controller. Also, the users joining/leaving actions inside the initCollaboratives() method have been modifed without clearing all cursors each time a user joins or leaves, allowing each user to have a unique, persistent cursor during their session.

Correct capitalization in namespaces
Fixed capitalization issue in namespaces across VisitsStatistics model and VisitTracker middleware. Made sure that all namespaces start with a capital 'A' to follow the conventions and avoid any potential errors or issues.

Implement visit tracking middleware and add legal routes
Added a new middleware, VisitTracker, to track and store visit statistics. Introduced a new 'legal' middleware group with associated routes to serve Terms of Service (ToS) and Privacy Policy pages. Also, added new 'VisitsStatistics' model to store visiting data and included the VisitTracker middleware into existing middleware groups.

Add partial payment feature and update various functions/classes
Including the feature for partial payments, the previous functions for layouts and models have been updated accordingly. Also, the 'findByUsername' function in the ApiController is changed to use email instead of username. The larecipe.php file's default version has been refactored from 1.0 to 1.1, and relevant files have been renamed accordingly. Besides, several miscellaneous updates have been made across the code for cleanup and consistency with implemented alterations.
